{"tid":2368658,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"NVIDIA考慮重新開始生產專用礦卡， 不過首先要弄清楚具體需求和影響","createTime":"2021-01-16T11:25:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T12:21:33.000Z","uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d57b8f1032640a46104a926033193970778fe36d","tid":2368658,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"據TomsHardware報導，NVIDIA正在考慮重新開始生產加密貨幣挖礦專用的安培架構顯卡。和曾經同樣用途的顯卡一樣，這些顯卡沒有顯示輸出，但有一個很現實的大問題是，是否有足夠的產能來滿足GPU的生產。<br />\n<br />\n自去年新冠病毒流行以來，隨著全球各地不少地方都有執行居家令這樣的政策，使得人們更多的時間待在家裡，玩電子遊戲的時間也變多了，導致對高性能顯卡和處理器還有遊戲機的需求大增，供應量趕不上需求量。特別是近期加密貨幣估值暴漲，導致礦工成批量購買顯卡，進一步加劇了GPU的供需矛盾。NVIDIA也很難判斷挖礦的GPU需求量到底對目前的銷售和價格有多大影響，不過正在考慮重啟專用礦卡的生產。<br />\n<br />\nNVIDIA首席財務官Colette Kress在第19屆摩根大通技術/汽車論壇會議上表示：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;如果加密貨幣有這樣強烈的需求，或者我們看到了一個值得參考的數字，也可以利用這個機會重啟專用礦卡的產品線，以解決持續的挖礦需求。我們不知道GeForce RTX 30系列GPU的終端產品需求中有多少來自挖礦，所以我們不相信它是我們今天業務的重要組成部分。遊戲市場的需求非常強勁，我們認為比我們目前的供應量更大。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n對於NVIDIA而言，能清楚地了解挖礦方面的需求是首要任務，也是有益而且必要的。由於礦工僅需要GPU的計算功能，並不需要顯示輸出，並且也不在乎所使用的GPU是否有禁用一些不必要的功能，例如視頻解碼處理等。NVIDIA可以將一些原本可能會處理掉的GPU作為專用礦卡生產，出售給有需要的礦工，不但減少了浪費，也降低了成本。"},{"pid":"b4d122f4d3207a6c5890ceeced9d990aaf449fa3","tid":2368658,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得18年既礦難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc22006f7f3203508f827106a5b461106f8bf4d","tid":2368658,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:30:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/89915/nvidia-is-considering-restarting-production-of-dedicated-mining-cards-but-first-we-must-figure-out-the-specific-needs-and-impact/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnvidia%2F89915%2Fnvidia-is-considering-restarting-production-of-dedicated-mining-cards-but-first-we-must-figure-out-the-specific-needs-and-impact%2F&d=urW02bDNsyUCiNuSwPhOyOf4PGxNkgPyFAzKtVao6pc%3D&h=2dc04684\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/89915/nvidia-is-considering-restarting-production-of-dedicated-mining-cards-but-first-we-must-figure-out-the-specific-needs-and-impact/</a>"},{"pid":"0a6c93ea509fcb2931ab5b7ad18aa84f48d8a253","tid":2368658,"uid":180538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:31:28.000Z","msg":"炒幣基金佬又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af1aeaf1abff38c6ce9b0d5ccedd9bd3201878b0","tid":2368658,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:32:29.000Z","msg":"喂出到3060 3070無得炒先啦屌你咩"},{"pid":"4b6aac46280191838700fd20dfe14eab98c42f9e","tid":2368658,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e26fc25fe31d5c54c1fcc9ac04b888a01b00b69","tid":2368658,"uid":328625,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T12:21:33.000Z","msg":"NVIDIA唔好搞啦 Bitcoin可以玩多幾耐 到你生產完出黎 Bitcoin都玩完啦 全部變哂蟹貨"}],"pinned":{"pid":"b4d122f4d3207a6c5890ceeced9d990aaf449fa3","tid":2368658,"uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"唔好唔記得18年既礦難<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}